N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 666.14 - Judicial review

State Regulations

Any person aggrieved by the issuance, denial, suspension, or revocation of a permit may within 30 days from the date of the
commissioner's order seek judicial review pursuant to article 78 of the Civil

Practice Law and Rules in the Supreme Court for the county in which the river
area is located. Notes
